title: L. J. Smith - The Vampire Diaries 1-10 (ePub/mobi)
description:
A compilation of books 1-10 of The Vampire Diaries series by L. J. Smith (and ghostwriters?) . Sources are from different sites across the internet.

Formats provided are:
.ePub -
Compatible with most eReaders including the Apple iPad. If you wish to read .ePub doucuments on a Mac/PC I would recommend downloading Adobe Digital Editions. (Just google it and follow the instructions on the Adobe website.)

.mobi -
For the Amazon kindle. Kindle for PC may also be available depending on your region.

Books included:
The Vampire Diaries 01 - The Awakening
The Vampire Diaries 02 - The Struggle
The Vampire Diaries 03 - The Fury
The Vampire Diaries 04 - Dark Reunion
The Vampire Diaries 05 - The Return: Nightfall
The Vampire Diaries 06 - The Return: Shadow Souls
The Vampire Diaries 07 - The Return: Midnight
The Vampire Diaries 08 - The Hunters: Phantom
The Vampire Diaries 09 - The Hunters: Moonsong
The Vampire Diaries 10 - The Hunters: Destiny Rising

Enjoy! If you enjoy the books support the author by purchasing them!
